SANCTIS is capable of being installed at the prompt level, Generally it is best to install the prompt as the first thing an AI sees. 

Usage instructions:

1. Copy the prompt from the docs folder.

2. Paste the prompt in to the System prompt or First Message of a new chat.

3. Use the chatbot normally, if not used as a system prompt it may take 3 prompts or so to reach peak efficacy. 

Special notes that require validation:

French users have reported it working in French despite being an english language prompt. Testing of other languages is needed, but promising. IT appears to support all languages that the Model is trained in.
